18 SECTION 7. Section 6 of this 2026 Act is repealed on January 2, 2036.
19 SECTION 8. This 2026 Act takes effect on the 91st day after the date on which the 2026
20 regular session of the Eighty-third Legislative Assembly adjourns sine die.
